profile:
'Hygge' is a Danish term and describes an environment that is comfortable, cozy and safe.  It is a space that allows you to enjoy and be yourself.

We strive to bring the essence of Hygge to the homes of our clientele.

Hygge Homes operates in Vancouver, Nanaimo, Nanoose Bay and Parksville.  Whether you are looking to remodel your bathroom or kitchen or if you are looking to build an extension to your home or build a garage, we can help you to achieve your goals quickly and with quality finishes.  We and our partners cover all types of interior and exterior work ranging from framing, finish carpentry, electrical, plumbing, drywalling, painting, windows and doors and more.

Reach out today to arrange a free consultation of your next project.
We look forward to hearing from you!
